    'relations_d_1' => "The company adopts the dual-track welfare system (the company and the welfare committee double-track welfare). In order to ensure that the company's salary and welfare system is superior to the industry level, it actively introduces various management systems, including: dual-track welfare system, perfect retirement Planning, comfortable working environment. ",
